This program is git frontend for eshell.
* Use synchronous process for fast response in remote host via tramp.
    * You cannot input ssh passphrase interactively. Use ssh-agent forwarding if necessary.
* Use emacs buffer instead of git pager.
* Some command output contain clickable text.
* Read git config from init.el.
    * You don't have to manage .gitconfig if you manage init.el.
    * You don't have to put .gitconfig on remote host.
* You don't have to learn key binding. Just type git command.
